      </item>
      <item>
        <p>
          <link href="https://aws.amazon.com/cli/">awscli</link>, a
          unified tool to manage your AWS services
        </p>
      </item>
      <item>
        <p>
          <link href="https://snakemake.readthedocs.io/en/stable/">snakemake</link>,
          a workflow management system to create reproducible and scalable
          data analyses
        </p>
      </item>
    </list>
